{"tid":1456154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣布 全民勇武 由呢刻開始","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:22:42.000Z","uid":285367,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"71b8dd91d2e96928b2e9c1e59414b1d6578115b8","tid":1456154,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:47:16.000Z","msg":"到底仲要有幾多人受傷<br />\n到底仲要有幾多人盲眼<br />\n到底仲要有幾多人比啲過街臭老鼠無理濫捕<br />\n次次都話全民憤怒了 我們連結了<br />\n最後呢？又係下一次再令香港人受傷 重傷 死 既鎮壓<br />\n屌你地肯醒未<br />\n<br />\n點解700萬人既基本人身安全<br />\n要比你區區幾萬濕鳩過街老鼠影響<br />\n搞到人心惶惶<br />\n<br />\n我宣傳 由依加開始 由今日機場開始 全民勇武大行動正式啟動<br />\n有市民被無理武力對待 法治治唔到佢地<br />\n就用人治<br />\n咁撚想香港變人治 我地香港人 就用香港人既力量  收佢地皮<br />\n<br />\n香港人 半點都不能少<br />\n共軍 一個都不能放"},{"pid":"1e714cd9a0b53e7f35f60b71d9b0daada7dfe788","tid":1456154,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:48:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90057fc6dea620be5615454fb9e92946acbb1fc9","tid":1456154,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:49:04.000Z","msg":"推撚爆佢 睇到好撚嬲"},{"pid":"b23f921a78a9a13d12473f23fc106951585ac146","tid":1456154,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:49:18.000Z","msg":"幫手推/散比機場手足聽"},{"pid":"d9f0642e992641633073f388c067735f2054fe5f","tid":1456154,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:49:28.000Z","msg":"香港人 忍夠了"},{"pid":"9fce21a601162115b4d1206afcb07a94534db308","tid":1456154,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:50:05.000Z","msg":"［兩軍交戰守則］偽裝成對方人員，被捕後可即場槍決<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456044</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"38bd0ee1905e7727b98bd70172c588867e276944","tid":1456154,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fce21a601162115b4d1206afcb07a94534db308","tid":1456154,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2